ckquote>無啦啦起火，又拉唔到人，真係唔信唔係政府做</blockquote><br />\n廢人訓街係真唔係冇原因<br />\n乜都政府</blockquote><br />\n香港正苦今時今日咁撚串唔係冇原因<br />\n乜都幫正苦護航<br />\n<br />\n唔好叫政府喇叫朝庭喇好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成句即刻通順好多，使到大家對閣下依挺人又了解多咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"211e18399180d4c807639ad14bd9300f1772a64e","tid":146030,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T00:08:05.000Z","msg":"唔係話有人係果到煮野咩？"},{"pid":"3691b90b140ee159bf8c9a409a6073d5bdce0068","tid":146030,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T00:15:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該立法禁止人訓街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果訓街就罰款，罰款唔交就破佢產</blockquote><br />\n瞓街都唔驚，點會驚破產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ba5aba116f6c73222a22e747d9c65aee61c7d9","tid":146030,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T00:17:08.000Z","msg":"新地及港鐵西南九龍港鐵南昌站上蓋重頭項目－匯璽（匯璽第2A期），涉逾千伙，屬近期大型新盤，發展商提速部署，將日內上樓書，本周一（3月6日）將率先開放4房連裝修示範單位及交樓標準，計劃月中賣樓。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a60f08911d4a03b048d6001a250dba3279f9639e","tid":146030,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T00:17:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>應該立法禁止人訓街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果訓街就罰款，罰款唔交就破佢產</blockquote><br />\n瞓街都唔驚，點會驚破產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\non99仲以為自己好醒"},{"pid":"030eb6508cbfd30bd62e6586d2e53c05f4f13f06","tid":146030,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T00:24:27.000Z","msg":"訓禮賓府"},{"pid":"67cb5339b86fe68da0a454d0e3d2f747de460b92","tid":146030,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T00:26